officialTitle: Patterns of Non-mass Enhancement of Breast MRI Using the BI-RADS Lexicon Fifth Edition With Histopathologic Correlation
primaryOutcomeMeasure: Patterns of non-mass enhancement on breast MRI
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* all female with mean age 50 ± 17 having breast MRI

Exclusion Criteria:

* Contraindications of MRI as pacemakers, aneurysmal clipping, retained metallic foreign bodies, or claustrophobic patients
* Pregnant women especially in the first trimester.
